p.d: A rich programme of laughter and good humour for this 9th edition of the Marrakech du Rire! With Jamel Debbouze as master of ceremonies, the show brings together Waly Dia, Florence Foresti, Caroline Vigneaux, Ary Abittan, Donel Jack'sman, Bun Hay Mean, Jarry, Ines Reg, Booder, Bigflo and Oli... Recorded at the El Badii Palace, Marrakech (Morocco) Directed by: Richard Valverde (France, 2019)
